OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with a few showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain. Dry for a time in
OL,8,Fthe early hours before a risk of
OL,9,Ffurther showers later on.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,12,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,13,FTurning brighter but with a risk of
OL,14,Ffurther showers in the afternoon, some
OL,15,Fpossibly heavy and thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
